{
  "texts": [
    "As alluded to in the previous paragraphs, LLMs can provide companionship and combat loneliness and social isolation.",
    "However, can it be used by therapists and healthcare professionals to aid during therapy?",
    "A review of previous-generation language models reported promising potential for use in mental health (Vaidyam et al., 2019).",
    "Despite limited data on its clinical efficacy, users dealing with mental health problems have been consulting ChatGPT (Eliot, 2023).",
    "Some studies investigated language models in the context of reminiscence therapy which involves engaging patients in recalling and discussing past experiences, often using tangible prompts like photographs or familiar objects (Khan et al., 2022)."
  ]
}